      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You utter a divine word, and burning radiance erupts from you. Each creature of your choice that you can see within range must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or take [[/r 1d6]] radiant damage.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>The spell's damage increases by [[/r 1d6]] when you reach 5th level ([[/r 2d6]]), 11th level ([[/r 3d6]]), and 17th level ([[/r 4d6]]).</p></div>",
